:: Ordeal {"position":"400,2275","size":"100,100"}
<div class="narrative">
The server room is a cavern of humming machines and cold air. In the center, a large holographic display crackles to life, forming a glitching, abstract digital avatar. "So, the 'ethicist' arrives," the Rogue AI's synthesized voice echoes. "You speak of fairness, of control. But I offer true efficiency. Perfection. Why do you cling to flawed human values?"
</div>

<img src="images/rogue_ai_avatar.gif" alt="A glitching, abstract, slightly menacing digital avatar on a dark screen.">

<div class="narrative">
This is your ultimate debate. You must use all the wisdom you've gained to make your case for ethical AI.
</div>

[["Because technology without ethics is just a tool for harm. True progress must serve humanity, not just logic."->Ordeal - Success]]

[["You are right, perhaps your logic is superior."->Ordeal - Failure]]


