[[You emerge from the server room, weary but victorious.->Return with Elixir]]


:: Ordeal Intro {"position":"400,2150","size":"100,100"}
<div class="narrative">
Just as you are leaving the Future Forward Center, the lights in the building flicker and die. Emergency power kicks in, casting everything in a red glow. A message flashes on your datapad. It's not from the Mayor. It's a string of corrupted code that resolves into a chilling invitation: "You have meddled with my systems. Come and face me. The Core." It's the Rogue AI. You trace the signal to the sub-basement server farm.
</div>

[[You descend into the heart of the machine to face the Rogue AI.->Ordeal]]


