<div class="narrative">
"Mayor, I... I don't know if I'm qualified to handle something this massive," you stammer. Overwhelmed, you retreat to your mentor's office at the Institute. Professor Elena’s study is a warm, cluttered room filled with the scent of old books and hot tea.
