<div class="narrative">
Professor Elena listens patiently, then places a heavy, leather-bound journal in your hands. A glowing circuit pattern is etched into its cover. "This is an AI Ethics Codex," she says. "It is for documenting your insights and choices. You are more capable than you think. You just need to begin." The Codex feels warm to the touch.
</div>

