:: Transition to Challenge 2 {"position":"775,1025","size":"100,100"}
<div class="narrative">
Your work at the school, for better or worse, has made waves. One evening, while reviewing notes in a bustling downtown café, you're approached by a woman with sharp, intelligent eyes and a no-nonsense demeanor. It's Lena, a well-known investigative journalist.
</div>

<img src="images/lena_journalist.gif" alt="A woman with sharp eyes, holding a futuristic recording device.">

<div class="narrative">
"You're Sophia?" she asks, not waiting for an answer. "I've been hearing about you. I have another story for you, one that goes much deeper than a school grading system." She slides her datapad across the table, displaying an article she’s working on about a biased hiring AI.
</div>

[[You agree to investigate with her.->Challenge 2 - TalentScan Intro]]


